#: ../../../internals/optimizer.rst:1323
msgid ""
"This is a very simple equivalence transform, but when we now run the "
"CommonSubexpressionEliminator, it will replace all occurrences of ``a_1`` by "
"``a`` (until ``a`` is re-assigned). The UnusedPruner will then eliminate the "
"variable ``a_1`` altogether and thus fully reverse the SSATransform."
