#: ../../../internals/optimizer.rst:1332
msgid "StackCompressor"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../internals/optimizer.rst:1334
msgid ""
"One problem that makes code generation for the Ethereum Virtual Machine hard "
"is the fact that there is a hard limit of 16 slots for reaching down the "
"expression stack. This more or less translates to a limit of 16 local "
"variables. The stack compressor takes Yul code and compiles it to EVM "
"bytecode. Whenever the stack difference is too large, it records the "
"function this happened in."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../internals/optimizer.rst:1341
msgid ""
"For each function that caused such a problem, the Rematerialiser is called "
"with a special request to aggressively eliminate specific variables sorted "
"by the cost of their values."
